# üìù Task Manager Project

This is a simple **Task Manager** project built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**.

It allows users to **add**, **edit**, **delete**, and **manage tasks** directly in the browser. All tasks are stored in **localStorage**, so your data persists even after refreshing.

